        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 The Perfect Game Formula</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200"><span class="text-white font-medium">Consistent 30+ pt turns + 2 bingos + going out first = 500+</span>. You don't need miracles — you need 13 turns of disciplined, informed play. The "perfect" game isn't superhuman. It's the absence of mistakes.</p>
